In the Matter of the Commission of Investigation of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Angelo De Cristofaro, Appellant.

Order, entered on September 11, 1963, unanimously affirmed. No opinion. The order of this court entered on February 6, 1964 is vacated. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, Valente, McNally and Bastow, JJ. [20 A D 2d 759.]
